    Some Shortcuts

    shortcuts.Rd

    Some simple shortcuts to model fitting engines.

    ## BayesX.
bayesx2(...)

## Gradient boosting.
boost2(...)

## Lasso.
lasso2(...)

    Arguments

    ...

    Arguments passed to bamlss and predict.bamlss.

    Value

    A bamlss object.

    See also

    bamlss, boost, lasso, BayesX

    Examples

    if (FALSE) ## Simulate data.
set.seed(123)
d <- GAMart()

## Estimate model.
f <- num ~ s(x1) + s(x2) + s(x3) + s(lon,lat)

## Boosted model.
b <- boost2(f, data = d)
